channel.title: Thymeleaf Forms :: Java Web Development
channel.description: Templates allow you to build generic forms. This lets you reuse the structure by rendering the same template with different labels and data. Thus, a single form can serve different purposes, saving you extra effort. Whenever possible, reuse existing templates! Start a New Project You will build a new project so you can practice with templates and forms. If you have not done so, commit and push any unsaved work from your hello-spring project.
